<br />

<br />
before you get buffed..  get selos runing and if you have clicky lev get that on too.. then buff up.. 
<br />

<br />
when you do him again.  you should have the first 2 spell spot open for his dots/root  if they land.. just shoot yourself with that cancel magic song.. that will get rid of those immediatly (don't play that song to long or you'll start eating into your buffs)
<br />

<br />
anyways.. think you should do ok..
