				<td colspan="2"><span>Just nailed him last night. He got one Blood Boil on me, but other than that he was cake. 
<br />

<br />
1 - Killed Cronies 1 by 1
<br />

<br />
2 - Got 2.5 min Selo's going, Got Purifying Chorus Going, Charmed the knucklehead and handed him the note.
<br />

<br />
I immediately started backpedaling and landed 2 Chants before reapplying Purifying Chorus. Then landed 3rd Chant and 1st Chant. Then Chorus again. Then 2nd Chant and 3rd Chant. He was all wrapped up in about 2 minutes. At 30% I charged him to stay in Melee Range and he did not poof out. He had me down to 85% or so (REGEN3 and a couple REGEN1 items), but otherwise was a cake walk. 
<br />

<br />
Anyone needing help with this on Torvonnilous, look me up. 
<br />

